name: NEW collection/Elegant black/cow leather shoulder bag
description:
New Autumn/Winter collection

This stunning shoulder bag is made from semi-glossy black leather and recycle cow leather, it is soft and has great touch.

This amazing shoulder bag has great quality, It is simple but stylish and elegant,I pay attention to every single details,hand-cut and hand-sewn.

100% Handmade in London

*All the items in my shop will be posted with recorded service*
